The nature and extent of procedures performed over the custom solution is dependent on the complexity of the solution. We use professional judgment when determining whether the custom solution is simple or complex.
In making our determination, we consider:
The method and software used to develop the custom solution (e.g. Alteryx, Tableau, Spotfire)
The technical knowledge, skills and experience needed to develop the solution
The nature and complexity of the solution’s functionality (e.g., calculations, categorizations, data processing, logical steps, queries, algorithms, inputs or outputs)
